title: AlphaTALKS Wall Street Breakfast December 11: What Moved Markets This Week
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Stocks posted their first winning week in a month. Major indexes rebounded early in the week after Pfizer (NYSE:PFE) and BioNTech (NASDAQ:BNTX) announced that three doses of their Covid-19 vaccine were effective in treating the omicron variant.
